:: Start
You are having, by any reasonable measure, the worst night of your life.

You do not yet know that it is also the last night of your life, or that this is, somehow, the good news.

A stranger sits down across from you. They smell like cold rain and old money. They look at you as though they already know exactly what you need to hear.

"I'm going to make you an offer," they say. "And I think — I really do think — you're going to say yes."

[[Choose who you are->Backgrounds]]

