:: Pitch: Love
//(Stub.)// The stranger promises eternal, unconditional, never-fading love. You have wanted exactly this for so long that you forgot it was a thing people could want.

[[Say yes->The Bite]]

:: Pitch: Power
//(Stub.)// The stranger offers you the power to be feared, adored, and impossible to ignore. Every face that ever looked through you — they will look *up*.

[[Say yes->The Bite]]

:: Pitch: Forever
//(Stub.)// The stranger offers you the one thing the doctors couldn't: more time. All of it. Every night there will ever be.

[[Say yes->The Bite]]

:: The Bite
You say yes.

You always say yes. The only question was ever *why*.

//(Stub: end of Chapter One. Next, you wake up absurdly, casually omnipotent — and an ancient society of equally omnipotent predators is already quite certain you are the one the prophecy promised. You have been a vampire for roughly four minutes. This seems like a lot.)//

